Default-OFF (deblock_cfg=None) => byte-identical to the current pipeline.
Minimal, additive: one optional kwarg + one preprocess call inside the realesrgan branch.
The cfg is threaded from MODE_CONFIG["quality"]["deblock_pre"] at the two run()/server
call sites (same pattern R8-E3's anchor_blend.patch used for anchor_blend_beta).

